    // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    // ══ TRAIT-LIBRARY-EXPANSION (spec: .docs/.tasks/open/TRAIT-LIBRARY-EXPANSION.md) ══
    // §1 · Attribute-combo traits — never a lone axis: every combo pairs two logically-linked
    // stats.jsonc axes, with a moderate (±15%) and a significant (±40-50%) rung on both sides.
    // Combat combos use `effects.combatMods` (combat statId → multiplier, the combat twin of
    // workSpeed). Resistances are EARNED, never granted by an abstract attribute — they live on
    // §3 coverings (naturalGear) and passive affinities only.
