    // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    // §4 · The eleven heritage LINEAGES (flattened, LINEAGES-II) — each is a pure MARKER trait
    // (legendary/mythic, `lineage` set) whose members are top-level traits tagged with the lineage id.
    // A born-in pawn gets the marker + ONE random S1 member (Culture.drawPawnTraits); the rest of the
    // tree is grown at seasonal growth events (lineageGrowthEvent). Member LINES are shared across
    // lineages where logical (adrenaline rides beast/werewolf alike), and AURAS appear ONLY here —
    // rare, lineage-gated, mutually exclusive (one conflict group), finite radius, throttled +
    // lingering application.
    // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
